What you need to know:

His best stint as Harambee Stars coach was his first between 2003-2004 when he won the 2002 Cecafa Senior Challenge Cup and qualified the team for the 2004 Africa Nations Cup finals in Tunisia.His worst stint has to be in 2010 when Kenya lost to Malawi, Uganda and Ethiopia at the Cecafa Senior Challenge Cup in Tanzania amidst unpaid allowance issues.